snippet.title: First Look at Amber Heard as Mera in JUSTICE LEAGUE Movie
snippet.description:
IGN.com has revealed the very first look at Amber Heard as the DC character Mera in Zack Snyder's upcoming "Justice League" movie coming in 2017. Her character rules the seas alongside Aquaman.

Cast: Gal Gadot, Ben Affleck, Jared Leto, Amber Heard, Jason Momoa, Ezra Miller, Ray Fisher
